  "text": "where z j denotes assignment of cell j to cluster k \u2208 {1, \u00b7 \u00b7 \u00b7 , K}. With integrating two data modalities (gene expression and epigenetic data), we improve inference of clusters (cell types). The scaling parameters \u03b1 j , \u03b2 j specific to cell j are used to normalize the data x x x j in downstream analysis by transforming to y y y j \u223c N (\u00b5 \u00b5 \u00b5 k , \u03a3 k ) according to the cluster it is assigned to z j = k, similar to [CITATION_1] . The plate model for Symphony is summarized in Figure 4 .",
